videos.description: Zion Williamson extends his arm on the drive to the basket and hits Markieff Morris in the midsection, sending him to the ground in pain.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion sends Morris to the hardwood with hit to midsection) 2021/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion sends Morris to the hardwood with hit to midsection

videos.description: Anthony Davis comes up with the block as Zion Williamson spins into the paint for a shot, but Williamson also lands an elbow on Montrezl Harrell's face.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion lands hard elbow to Harrell's face) 2021/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion lands hard elbow to Harrell's face

videos.description: Things get spicy between Steven Adams and LeBron James and referees hit them with double technicals to calm the jawing down.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Adams, LeBron called for double technicals) 2021/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adams, LeBron called for double technicals

videos.description: Zion Williamson elevates on the baseline and double-clutches in mid-air to avoid Anthony Davis and throw down a sweet dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion throws down sweet double-clutch dunk) 2021/01/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion throws down sweet double-clutch dunk
